#Subtitle2
1
00:18,138 --> 00:24,453
Milly sat under the apple tree and watched the [rain clouds] sweep over [the hills].
 -- 米莉坐在蘋果樹下，看著[雨雲]掠過[山丘]。

2
00:24,453 --> 00:27,265
What a [wet] day!
 -- 多麼[潮濕]的一天！

3
00:27,265 --> 00:31,610
She ate an apple and waited for the rain to stop.
 -- 她吃了一個蘋果，等著雨停。

4
00:31,610 --> 00:33,651
Soon it did.
 -- 很快就成功了。

5
00:33,651 --> 00:39,946
The sky [turned blue] again, and the Sun [shone], warm and golden.
 -- 天空又[變藍]了，太陽[照耀]著，溫暖而金色。

6
00:39,946 --> 00:43,553
Then she saw the rainbow. 
 -- 然後她看到了彩虹。

7
00:43,553 --> 00:49,116
It began as an [explosion] of light, high in the clouds.
 -- 它開始時，就像光線在高處雲層[爆炸]。

8
00:49,116 --> 00:57,240
The sky filled with [dazzling colors]: blue, orange, green and purple.
 -- 天空充滿了[耀眼的色彩]：藍色、橙色、綠色和紫色。

9
00:57,240 --> 01:03,488
Then both ends of the rainbow began to fall to Earth...
 -- 然後彩虹的兩端開始落到地球上……

10
01:03,488 --> 01:08,263
The rainbow landed in the garden.
 -- 彩虹降落在花園裡。

11
01:08,263 --> 01:14,95
‘Wow!’ Milly went closer and touched the rainbow. 
 -- “哇！”米莉走近，摸了摸彩虹。

12
01:14,95 --> 01:17,444
She felt nothing, just air.
 -- 她什麼都感覺不到，只有空氣。

13
01:17,444 --> 01:21,832
But the colors moved [beneath] her fingers.
 -- 但是顏色在她的手指[下]移動。

14
01:21,832 --> 01:29,133
When she looked up, the rainbow seemed to be [stretching] on and on into space.
 -- 當她抬頭看時，彩虹似乎一直[延伸]到太空中。

15
01:29,133 --> 01:35,139
'What would happen if I [stepped inside] it?' she wondered.
 -- “如果我[走進去]會發生什麼？” 她想知道。

16
01:35,139 --> 01:37,857
There was only one way to find out...
 -- 只有一種方法可以查明...

17
01:37,857 --> 01:40,146
She stepped inside.
 -- 她走進去。

18
01:40,146 --> 01:44,246
It was beautiful! 
 -- 它過去挺美！

19
01:44,246 --> 01:46,463
And very quiet. 
 -- 而且很安靜。

20
01:46,463 --> 01:48,426
Milly couldn’t hear anything.
 -- 米莉什麼也聽不見。

21
01:48,426 --> 01:50,567
She [looked up]. 
 -- 她[抬起頭]。

22
01:50,567 --> 01:53,507
The rainbow seemed to go on forever...
 -- 彩虹似乎永遠持續下去……

23
01:53,507 --> 01:57,737
WHOOSH! Milly was [sucked up] by the rainbow. 
 -- 嗖！ 米莉被彩虹[吸了上去]。

24
01:57,737 --> 01:59,801
It was a [tunnel] of light. 
 -- 那是一條光之[隧道]。

25
01:59,801 --> 02:03,327
She [whizzed along] like a button up a [vacuum cleaner]. 
 -- 她像按下[吸塵器]上的按鈕後一樣，[呼嘯而過]。

26
02:03,327 --> 02:06,234
Wind [whistled past] her ears. 
 -- 風從她耳邊[呼嘯而過]。

27
02:06,234 --> 02:14,233
She [tumbled] over and over but didn’t hurt herself: she was carried on a [soft cushion] of air. 
 -- 她一遍又一遍地[翻滾]，但沒有傷到自己：她被一個[柔軟的氣墊]支撐著。

28
02:14,233 --> 02:19,134
Up and up and up she went, so fast.
 -- 她走得越來越快，越來越快。

29
02:19,134 --> 02:22,153
But rainbows go up...
 -- 但彩虹升起...

30
02:22,153 --> 02:24,928
and rainbows come down. 
 -- 彩虹降臨。

31
02:24,928 --> 02:29,446
Soon she was falling down the far side of the rainbow. 
 -- 很快她就從彩虹的另一邊掉下來了。

32
02:29,446 --> 02:31,627
She could see green below.
 -- 她可以看到下面的綠色。

33
02:31,627 --> 02:36,369
Green grass, rushing up to meet her, faster and faster...
 -- 綠草，迎面撲來，越來越快……

34
02:36,369 --> 02:41,760
BUMP! She landed hard, but nothing was broken.
 -- 撞！ 她重重地落地，但沒有損壞任何東西。

35
02:41,760 --> 02:44,155
Milly stood up. 
 -- 米莉站了起來。

36
02:44,155 --> 02:49,324
She was on the other side of the valley, standing on a [steep] green hill.
 -- 她在山谷的另一邊，站在[陡峭的]青山上。

37
02:49,324 --> 02:52,76
She could see her house, far away.
 -- 她可以看到她的房子，很遠。

38
02:52,76 --> 02:56,704
It was like a tiny white box with a rainbow in the garden.
 -- 它就像一個白色的小盒子，花園裡有彩虹。

39
02:56,704 --> 03:02,465
Everything was [calm and peaceful] and very lovely...
 -- 一切都[平靜祥和]，非常可愛……

40
03:02,465 --> 03:10,133
WHOOSH! Suddenly she was shooting back through the rainbow, faster than a firework.
 -- 嗖！ 突然間，她從彩虹中被射了回來，比煙火還快。

41
03:10,133 --> 03:14,957
Red, blue, yellow ... stripes of light, flashing by.
 -- 紅、藍、黃……一道道光紋，一閃而過。

42
03:14,957 --> 03:21,372
Up, up, up she went and down, down, down... 
 -- 她往上，往上，往上，往下，往下，往下……

43
03:21,372 --> 03:26,345
BUMP. She landed back in her own garden.
 -- 碰。 她回到了自己的花園。

44
03:26,345 --> 03:29,790
'Oww...!’ Milly [groaned]. 
 -- “哇……！”米莉[呻吟]道。

45
03:29,790 --> 03:33,268
‘I am going to be so [bruised] tomorrow.'
 -- “我明天會[瘀青]。”

46
03:33,268 --> 03:35,846
Then she had a thought...
 -- 然後她有了一個想法……

47
03:35,846 --> 03:41,120
'GOLD! There is always gold at the end of a rainbow!'
 -- '金子！ 彩虹盡頭總有黃金！

48
03:41,120 --> 03:45,139
She dropped to her knees and started to [dig].
 -- 她跪下來開始[挖]。

49
03:45,139 --> 03:51,669
The earth flew out behind her, covering the grass with stones and soil.
 -- 泥土在她身後飛出，草地上佈滿了用石頭和泥土。

50
03:51,669 --> 03:57,754
'Come on, come on! It must be here somewhere...'
 -- '好啦好啦！ 它一定在這兒的某個地方……”

51
03:57,754 --> 04:00,840
She went deeper and deeper. 
 -- 她越挖越深。

52
04:00,840 --> 04:06,352
Then she saw something [shiny], under her fingertips.
 -- 然後她看到指尖下有什麼[閃閃發亮]的東西。

53
04:06,352 --> 04:07,860
She pulled it out.
 -- 她把它拉了出來。

54
04:07,860 --> 04:10,187
'Gold...'
 -- '金子...'

55
04:10,187 --> 04:14,536
Milly [stared at] it, [breathless with excitement].
 -- 米莉[盯]著它，[興奮得喘不過氣來]。

56
04:14,536 --> 04:20,821
 It was a [golden coin], bigger than usual money and much heavier. 
 -- 那是一枚[金幣]，比平常的錢要大，也重得多。

57
04:20,821 --> 04:22,565
She [rubbed it clean]. 
 -- 她[把它擦乾淨]。

58
04:22,565 --> 04:29,706
There were words written on it: [Make a wish] before the rainbow [fades].
 -- 上面寫著：在彩虹[消失]之前[許個願]。

59
04:29,706 --> 04:37,297
'Oh wow!' she said. 'This is [amazing]! A wish!'
 -- “哦哇！” 她說。 '這真太[了不起]了！ 一個心願！'

60
04:37,297 --> 04:43,113
Her head began to fill with ideas, everything she could wish for.
 -- 她的腦子裡開始充滿了想法，她所希望的一切。

61
04:43,113 --> 04:46,138
But then she saw something. 
 -- 但隨後她看到了什麼。

62
04:46,138 --> 04:49,264
The rainbow was starting to fade.
 -- 彩虹開始褪色。

63
04:49,264 --> 04:52,303
It was going thin at the edges.
 -- 它的邊緣變薄了。

64
04:52,303 --> 04:57,837
'No! I haven't made up my mind! Please - wait!'
 -- '不！ 我還沒想好！ 請稍等！'

65
04:57,837 --> 05:00,658
But the rainbow didn't wait.
 -- 但是彩虹沒有等。

66
05:00,658 --> 05:06,180
It was fading. Going away, and taking her wish with it.
 -- 它正在褪色。 離開，並帶著她的願望。

67
05:06,180 --> 05:10,676
'No! I’ll make my wish soon. Just a moment, please!'
 -- '不！ 我很快就會許願完成。 請稍等片刻！'

68
05:10,676 --> 05:14,34
But still the rainbow was fading. 
 -- 但彩虹仍在消退。

69
05:14,34 --> 05:17,491
The golden coin was getting hot in her hand.
 -- 金幣在她手中越來越燙。

70
05:17,491 --> 05:22,242
'Ohh....! Choose... choose... Yes. YES! I have it!'
 -- 啊……！ 選擇……選擇……是的。 是的！ 我有它！

71
05:22,242 --> 05:27,652
Milly closed her eyes and made her wish and VOOMF!
 -- 米莉閉上眼睛許下了她的願望，VOOMF！

72
05:27,652 --> 05:32,224
The rainbow disappeared, and so did the golden coin.
 -- 彩虹消失了，金幣也消失了。

73
05:32,224 --> 05:35,668
Milly hardly dared to move.
 -- 米莉幾乎不敢動彈。

74
05:35,668 --> 05:38,583
Had her wish come true?
 -- 她的願望實現了嗎？

75
05:38,583 --> 05:40,45
Maybe.
 -- 或許。

76
05:40,45 --> 05:41,717
She looked up. 
 -- 她抬起頭。

77
05:41,717 --> 05:44,299
The sky was peacock blue.
 -- 天空是孔雀藍。

78
05:44,299 --> 05:48,215
The Sun was golden, warm on her face.
 -- 陽光是金色的，溫暖地照在她的臉上。

79
05:48,215 --> 05:51,267
Such a beautiful day.
 -- 多麼美好的一天。

80
05:51,267 --> 05:54,423
Such a beautiful world.
 -- 如此美麗的世界。

81
05:54,423 --> 06:02,369
'Even if the wish doesn't come true, I am a very lucky girl,' she said.
 -- “即使願望沒有實現，我也是一個非常幸運的女孩，”她說。

82
06:02,369 --> 06:06,347
And she smiled.
 -- 她笑了。

83
06:06,347 --> 06:06,347
 -- 
